Package com.google.common.util.concurrent

Interface FutureCallback<V>

  • @Deprecated(since="2022-12-01")
public interface FutureCallback<V>
    Deprecated.
    The Google Guava Core Libraries are deprecated and will not be part of the AEM SDK after April 2023
    A callback for accepting the results of a Future computation asynchronously.

    To attach to a ListenableFuture use Futures.addCallback(com.google.common.util.concurrent.ListenableFuture<V>, com.google.common.util.concurrent.FutureCallback<? super V>).

    Since:
    10.0
